      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到您提到了安全属性——Projet 应该配置 Security_Firewall 对吧？那其他几个实体的安全策略怎么分配？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Projet",
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Projet 用防火墙。Plateforme 作为入口层，用 Security_OAuth2。Porteur 是核心资金载体，必须上 Security_ZeroTrust。剩下的 Utilisateur、Parrain 还有 Adresse 本身都用 Security_IntrusionDetection 做入侵检测。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Porteur",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Utilisateur",
        "Parrain",
        "Adresse",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，六个类都创建好了，安全属性也标注完成。现在来处理关系——Plateforme 作为平台方，应该关联多个用户角色吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Utilisateur",
        "Parrain",
        "Porteur"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Plateforme 到 Utilisateur、Parrain、Porteur 都是一对多的平台入驻关系，箭头指向角色方。另外每个角色都要关联 Adresse，一对一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Utilisateur",
        "Parrain",
        "Porteur",
        "Adresse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Plateforme 0..1 指向多个 Utilisateur 0..*，同样方式指向 Parrain 和 Porteur。然后 Utilisateur、Parrain、Porteur 各自 0..1 关联 Adresse 0..1。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Utilisateur",
        "Parrain",
        "Porteur",
        "Adresse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。还有 Plateforme 自己也要关联 Adresse，平台地址一对一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加 Plateforme 到 Adresse 的关联。现在 Projet 的关系怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Plateforme",
        "Adresse",
        "Projet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Projet 比较特殊。一个 Porteur 可以发起多个 Projet，所以 Porteur 到 Projet 是一对多，箭头指向 Porteur。另外 Parrain 可以赞助多个 Projet，也是一对多，箭头指向 Parrain。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Porteur",
        "Projet",
        "Parrain"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有个细节：Parrain 到 Projet 您说的是 0..* 还是 0..1？ sponsor 关系通常是可选的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Parrain",
        "Projet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Parrain 可以赞助多个项目，所以是 0..*。但 Porteur 和 Projet 的关系更紧密，一个 Projet 只能有一个 Porteur，所以 Porteur 那边是 0..1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Parrain",
        "Projet",
        "Porteur"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有关系已绘制完成。我检查一下：Parrain 和 Adresse 之间还有一条双向的一对一关联，这个需要保留吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
